comment:
* Semi-immutable container for a single capture request and associated information,
 * the only mutable characteristic of this container is whether or not is has been
 * marked as "failed" using {@code #failRequest}.

methods.name: public int getRequestId()
methods.comment: * Return the request id for the contained {@link CaptureRequest}.

methods.name: public boolean isRepeating()
methods.comment: * Returns true if the contained request is repeating.

methods.name: public int getSubsequeceId()
methods.comment: * Return the subsequence id for this request.

methods.name: public long getFrameNumber()
methods.comment: * Returns the frame number for this request.

methods.name: public Collection<Surface> getHolderTargets()
methods.comment: * Returns a read-only collection of the surfaces targeted by the contained request.

methods.name: public boolean hasJpegTargets()
methods.comment: * Returns true if any of the surfaces targeted by the contained request require jpeg buffers.

methods.name: public boolean hasPreviewTargets()
methods.comment:
* Returns true if any of the surfaces targeted by the contained request require a
     * non-jpeg buffer type.

methods.name: public int numJpegTargets()
methods.comment: * Return the number of jpeg-type surfaces targeted by this request.

methods.name: public int numPreviewTargets()
methods.comment: * Return the number of non-jpeg-type surfaces targeted by this request.

methods.name: public boolean jpegType(Surface s) throws LegacyExceptionUtils.BufferQueueAbandonedException
methods.comment:
* Returns true if the given surface requires jpeg buffers.
     *
     * @param s a {@link android.view.Surface} to check.
     * @return true if the surface requires a jpeg buffer.

methods.name: public boolean requestFailed()
methods.comment: * Return {@code true} if this request failed.

methods.name: public void setOutputAbandoned()
methods.comment: * Mark at least one of this request's output surfaces is abandoned.

methods.name: public boolean isOutputAbandoned()
methods.comment: * Return if any of this request's output surface is abandoned.
